scene.message:
Female Student: What do we do,{nl}
there's no exit anywhere.{nl}
We're trapped in here!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Before long, demons will come.{waitkey}Hordes of demons will come{nl}
and torment us to death!!{waitkey}{ret}

Female Student: Even if you{nl}
beat the Snow Queen, there{nl}
are still other strong{nl}
demons left, right!?{waitkey}{clearbox}It's all over...{waitkey}{ret}

Female Student: Who was it{nl}
that said "the school is{nl}
safe"?{waitkey}I want to go home...{waitkey}{ret}

Female Student: Why can't we{nl}
get outside yet?{waitkey}{clearbox}Don't tell me all we can do{nl}
is wait here to freeze to{nl}
death?{waitkey}{clearbox}I won't have it! There's so{nl}
much I still want to do!{waitkey}{ret}

Satori: It's all over now.{waitkey}We're all going to die someday{nl}
anyway... this just moves it{nl}
up a little.{waitkey}{clearbox}We get to end our lives still{nl}
beautiful, so we ought to{nl}
thank the Snow Queen.{waitkey}{ret}

Satori: Keeping my eyes{nl}
closed like this, it's as if{nl}
everything has stopped{nl}
breathing.{waitkey}{clearbox}So very quiet.{waitkey}Somehow... I'm getting{nl}
sleepy... it... seems......{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: What gloomy people.{nl}
Let's hurry on. They're{nl}
bringing me down too.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Still going on like{nl}
that. It's depressing — let's{nl}
get out, quick.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Honestly, Ayase's{nl}
anxious too. I crack jokes{nl}
and all, but...{waitkey}{clearbox}I keep wondering if we can{nl}
really save Ms. Saeko.{waitkey}{clearbox}I mean, we're still just high{nl}
schoolers! What can we even{nl}
do!?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: {ctl07:0}, you're really{nl}
strong, huh. You don't{nl}
complain even once.{waitkey}{clearbox}That side of you — Ayase's{nl}
impressed.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: To admit defeat before{nl}
even acting...{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll fight to the very end!{nl}
For my own future, too.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Don't worry.{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll melt the Queen's icy{nl}
heart with my smoldering{nl}
gaze, you'll see.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Don't worry.{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll melt the Queen's icy{nl}
heart with my smoldering{nl}
gaze, you'll see.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: In extreme situations,{nl}
you catch a glimpse of human{nl}
nature, don't you.{waitkey}Heh...{waitkey}{ret}

